DISTRICT XI BASEBALL CHAMPIONSHIPS

presented by ST. LUKE’S UNIVERSITY HEALTH NETWORK

2024-25

District XI will conduct baseball tournaments in six separate classifications. There will be tournaments in Classes "A" through "6A" if there are sufficient eligible teams. Reference should be made to the most recent P.I.A.A. Handbook for the classification status of member schools.

Game Day Information for Coaches

Please click on the classification on the left to see the current power rankings.
